Enough.

296
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,800
[Fang Yan]

297
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:41,240
[Superstar, this is my third wish.]

298
00:18:41,320 --> 00:18:42,560
[I hope you can come here.]

299
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:44,620
[Shi Meng has something to tell you.]

300
