Do you have any secrets...

315
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:30,120
that you can tell me?

316
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,640
What secret do I have?

317
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:35,450
The secret between you and Shi Yi
when you were young.

318
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,640
Come with me.

319
