at this time?

435
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,160
It's not suitable.

436
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:31,650
No, it's Shi Yi.

437
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:33,200
I wanted to arrange...

438
00:29:33,280 --> 00:29:35,440
